{"tid":1747961,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果有天","createTime":"2019-11-23T12:37:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T13:59:48.000Z","uid":333890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ed96bf9a33dc4e5d867b0ecf29f7efa35ded18ee","tid":1747961,"uid":333890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:37:14.000Z","msg":"<strong>明天投建制的<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍絲</span>們，如果有天你</strong><br />\n<br />\n去醫院做手術，之後腎臓不見了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買奶粉給小孩喝，變了大頭嬰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n被公司克扣人工，反被告誹謗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屋子被強拆，用作建小白象公廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得罪惡人，第二日變死因無可疑浮屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n百病纏身，但要先付數萬才能治療<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有錢行街購物，遭公安嫉妒一棍打頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n社會信用評分低，連坐巴士也不能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想吃豬肉，發現含有大陸來源非洲豬瘟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不小心看禁書禁網，被送到集中營再教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n言談間表示不滿，被判監三年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n終於覺悟而反抗時，被老解用坦克輾死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不要害怕，是你爭取的。</span></span>"},{"pid":"a7dd7fb34183686fd9145aadf541b108b6a7f7ae","tid":1747961,"uid":256505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:40:53.000Z","msg":"和理非唔知點抗爭？唔想放棄？<br />\n 入黎進修下 和理非天書<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［進擊的和理非］<br />\n和理非武裝化 - 知識篇 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/eyJDKT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/eyJDKT</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9250a968c781d257fe4f063c5b0b3ba2031a4d7e","tid":1747961,"uid":288312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:42:07.000Z","msg":"[深度數據分析] 你知道嗎？多你一票好多<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ezEbiS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ezEbiS</a>"},{"pid":"bca74c0a2652c2f6ee4d11cf12f9b0cb632fe537","tid":1747961,"uid":333890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:57:19.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"af38f5717c8658cc32c1aebd411a0291a5122702","tid":1747961,"uid":333890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:57:29.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"e095a7813baf41da392fbffd76a3eab92dd5e665","tid":1747961,"uid":333890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:57:42.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"f17f8697d2f9341c05f554c6e45dc656e2d0fbbd","tid":1747961,"uid":333890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:57:52.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"4b4d6ab83dd7e188fa2e120923e0fe774e5cf75e","tid":1747961,"uid":333890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:58:04.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"cf3270bac905876791227c605159918a388afeb3","tid":1747961,"uid":333890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:58:32.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"2cd8e03b4c4358c5ecae9ef02da2cc3360c5be57","tid":1747961,"uid":333890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:58:43.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"417112c1101814591d03045c4de6f9530b3feec2","tid":1747961,"uid":333890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:58:53.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"b338cc8e33d2b2a10b4c7b1501f78a89399f0fd4","tid":1747961,"uid":333890,"like":0,"dislike":0